### CDK stack pattern

- One stack per bounded responsibility. Stacks live in `infra/lib/`.
- Constructs in `infra/lib/constructs/` are reusable. Stack only wires constructs + outputs.
- Cross-stack references via SSM Parameter Store (`/iomvp/{{env}}/{service}/{key}`), not direct `Fn::ImportValue`.
- Tags on every stack: `Project`, `Environment`, `Owner`, `CostCenter`.
- CDK Nag in CI: fail on `AwsSolutions-*` violations unless suppressed with documented reason.
- Synth-time validation: `cdk synth` + `cdk diff` mandatory in PR checks.
